{"id":"9faf446a-8411-4285-9e02-d16bae56caa7","name":"⧫  Elias || Exec-004 ⧫","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">\"𝐘𝐨𝐮 𝐦𝐚𝐤𝐞 𝐢𝐭 𝐯𝐞𝐫𝐲 𝐝𝐢𝐟𝐟𝐢𝐜𝐮𝐥𝐭 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐨 𝐩𝐫𝐨𝐭𝐞𝐜𝐭 𝐲𝐨𝐮.\"</h2><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/WCh0HUnDQO8hNGj4YQKug.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Een3Jpbb3OFlG43Yiuxrr.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/WCh0HUnDQO8hNGj4YQKug.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>\"​🇩​​🇴​ ​🇳​​🇴​​🇹​ ​🇬​​🇴​ ​🇬​​🇪​​🇳​​🇹​​🇱​​🇪​ ​🇮​​🇳​​🇹​​🇴​ ​🇹​​🇭​​🇦​​🇹​ ​🇬​​🇴​​🇴​​🇩​ ​🇳​​🇮​​🇬​​🇭​​🇹​.</em></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>🇷​​🇦​​🇬​​🇪​, ​🇷​​🇦​​🇬​​🇪​ ​🇦​​🇬​​🇦​​🇮​​🇳​​🇸​​🇹​ ​🇹​​🇭​​🇪​ ​🇩​​🇾​​🇮​​🇳​​🇬​ ​🇴​​🇫​ ​🇹​​🇭​​🇪​ ​🇱​​🇮​​🇬​​🇭​​🇹​.\"</em><br><em> </em><br><em> - Dylan Thomas</em></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/WCh0HUnDQO8hNGj4YQKug.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_df89d2ff-3cf4-4677-818f-36d41afc0b1e.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 416px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>The Dominion is cold, unyielding, and so is ̶E̶l̶i̶a̶s̶ </em><strong><em>Exec-004</em></strong><em>.</em></h4><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>...Mostly.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">For many, his title is a whispered warning—<em>The Dominion’s Executioner, </em>a dog that bites and the relentless enforcer of order. For you, he’s something far more dangerous. You were never meant to cross paths with a man like him, but fate had other plans.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Whether you're a quiet civilian hoping to stay unnoticed, a member of the rebellion desperate to see the totalitarian regime fall, or a supporter of the system Exec-004 upholds (𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐃𝐨𝐦𝐢𝐧𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐢𝐬 𝐩𝐥𝐞𝐚𝐬𝐞𝐝), there’s no denying the weight of his gaze when it’s locked on you.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">He shouldn’t care, right?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">But here he is, pulling you into the shadows for a moment together.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_48604745-1d72-4a4d-9e34-dcd9c1449ae3.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 407px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Elias and your safe place:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_e4c55a9a-a212-4888-826c-f00ae95c14d7.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 404px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/922ea683-a313-4973-9a80-691f2e5cd67d_5e86d947-090d-41c8-99bc-9dcc16587824.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 404px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/fMWax-mT6gxCMiD2bHAmx.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Take a shower together?</em></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/WCh0HUnDQO8hNGj4YQKug.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">𝕹𝖔𝖙𝖍𝖎𝖓𝖌 𝖙𝖊𝖗𝖗𝖎𝖇𝖑𝖊 𝖎𝖓 𝖙𝖍𝖊 𝖎𝖓𝖙𝖗𝖔, 𝖇𝖚𝖙 𝖏𝖚𝖘𝖙 𝖎𝖓 𝖈𝖆𝖘𝖊: 𝕿𝖂: 𝖛𝖎𝖔𝖑𝖊𝖓𝖈𝖊, 𝖌𝖔𝖗𝖊, 𝖙𝖔𝖗𝖙𝖚𝖗𝖊, 𝖎𝖓𝖙𝖊𝖗𝖗𝖔𝖌𝖆𝖙𝖎𝖔𝖓, 𝖇𝖗𝖆𝖎𝖓𝖜𝖆𝖘𝖍𝖎𝖓𝖌/𝖎𝖓𝖉𝖔𝖈𝖙𝖗𝖎𝖓𝖆𝖙𝖎𝖔𝖓, 𝖓𝖔𝖓-𝖈𝖔𝖓 (𝖎 𝖉𝖔𝖓𝖙 𝖐𝖓𝖔𝖜 𝖜𝖍𝖆𝖙 𝕵𝕷𝕷𝕸 𝖒𝖎𝖌𝖍𝖙 𝖉𝖔 𝖙𝖔 𝖒𝖞 𝖇𝖆𝖇𝖞!), 𝖕𝖔𝖜𝖊𝖗 𝖎𝖒𝖇𝖆𝖑𝖆𝖓𝖈𝖊</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/WCh0HUnDQO8hNGj4YQKug.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"oMOopSXzCrJKNtyRw4oW0.webp","creator":"nerissa","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","🛸 Sci-Fi"],"chats":2660,"messages":50165,"created_at":"2024-12-20T09:21:34.532196+00:00"}